  "text": "Heuristic algorithm based on the discrete model is proposed in reference [CITATION_1] to deal with the UA-FLP. is approach divided the district into some small squares with a fixed area, and each facility was allocated some numbers of squares most close to its area by use of heuristic algorithm. As shown in Figure 1 , the grid size determines the precision of the facility representation; the smaller the grid size, the more precise the facility representation. e facility shape was also represented well by this approach. But, the time consumption is great to calculate the interference between facilities during the detailed layout process. Also, this approach is easy to produce facility layout with irregular shape. By far, the most commonly used UA-FLP model is mainly based on block diagram with unequal area as depicted in [CITATION_2] .",
